author: Joshua Fluke
description:
It’s that time of year again — when “team bonding” means pretending to have fun in front of your boss dressed as a Power Ranger. Every October, LinkedIn turns into a cringe carnival of executives forcing people to smile for content.

From pizza parties that double as “culture,” to employees getting marched through the hallway for engagement metrics, this is what happens when your office tries to go viral.

#CorporateCringe #LinkedInLunatics #OfficeCulture #JoshuaFluke
